  <p><app>GNOME Chess</app> is GNOME's chess game. It lets you play against the
  computer or another person. GNOME Chess can detect known
  <link xref="chess-engines">chess engines</link> for computer players. It also
  allows you to play against other people over a <link xref="chess-engines">
  network</link>.</p>

